    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

) AS "t"

    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"

    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"

) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

) AS "t"

FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"

FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"

SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

) AS "t"

FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"

    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"

    ORDER BY "u"."CreatedTime" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN "UserExtension" AS "u0" ON "t"."Id" = "u0"."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u1"."UserId", "u1"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u1"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u1"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."CreatedTime" DESC, "t"."Id", "u0"."UserId", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

2021-01-10 19:52:16.108 +08:00 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"

) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"

) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

2021-01-10 20:10:50.708 +08:00 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"
2021-01-10 20:10:50.712 +08:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"

) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"

) AS "t"

FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"

    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

2021-01-10 20:12:46.940 +08:00 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"
2021-01-10 20:12:46.944 +08:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"

SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."Avatar", "t"."CreatedTime", "t"."Email", "t"."EmailConfirmed", "t"."Gender", "t"."IsDeleted", "t"."IsLocked", "t"."NickName", "t"."Password", "t"."PasswordEncryptKey", "t"."PhoneNumber", "t"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "t"."UpdatedTime", "t"."UserName", "t0"."Id", "t0"."CreatedTime", "t0"."IsDefault", "t0"."IsDeleted", "t0"."IsLocked", "t0"."IsSuperAdministrator", "t0"."Name", "t0"."Remark", "t0"."UpdatedTime", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId"
FROM (
    SELECT "u"."Id", "u"."Avatar", "u"."CreatedTime", "u"."Email", "u"."EmailConfirmed", "u"."Gender", "u"."IsDeleted", "u"."IsLocked", "u"."NickName", "u"."Password", "u"."PasswordEncryptKey", "u"."PhoneNumber", "u"."PhoneNumberConfirmed", "u"."UpdatedTime", "u"."UserName"
    FROM "User" AS "u"
    WHERE (NOT ("u"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("u"."IsLocked")) AND ("u"."Id" = 1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "r"."Id", "r"."CreatedTime", "r"."IsDefault", "r"."IsDeleted", "r"."IsLocked", "r"."IsSuperAdministrator", "r"."Name", "r"."Remark", "r"."UpdatedTime", "u0"."UserId", "u0"."RoleId"
    FROM "UserRole" AS "u0"
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS "r" ON "u0"."RoleId" = "r"."Id"
    WHERE NOT ("r"."IsDeleted") AND NOT ("r"."IsLocked")
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."UserId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."UserId", "t0"."RoleId", "t0"."Id"
